      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario geometry, loading, and boundary conditions are representative of the COU; any differences between validation and COU scenarios are documented and their impact assessed.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the identical screw-rod construct geometry and test fixture as specified in the COU. F1717 test configuration is the regulatory standard for this device class. The validation scenario is judged highly representative of the COU with no substantive differences in geometry, material, or loading mode."
