    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy pre-specified quantitative acceptance criteria (percent difference <10%, E/uval <1.96). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels; the single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is mitigated by the quasi-static rate insensitivity of the titanium alloy system and the regulatory standing of the F1717 protocol. The overall credibility evidence package is judged sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission decision.",
